The only part I could possibly see troublesome is the body shield-if I am reading this correctly if the warrior used body shield on another character, not only his abilities (attack taunt ect) are unusable for 20 seconds but the person he is using the discipline on is also unable to use his abilities? <br>
<br>
In an ideal world this would work out fine, but this could be viewed as having too much power over somebody else.....could kinda be like porting people places without asking, or resing somebody for 0 experience without asking ect. Maybe if a box came up to the person being body shielded that asked them if they wanted shielded or something along those lines would work better? Can't think of any immediate solutions, was just wondering if you took that into consideration while thinking of these new abilities. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub21.ezboard.com/ffiresofheaven32084frm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=29.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub21.ezboard.com/ffiresofheaven32084frm1.showNextMessage?topicID=29.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/ffiresofheaven32084frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=29.topic&index=50><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/ffiresofheaven32084frm1.emailToFriend?topicID=29.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/ffiresofheaven32084frm1.threadControl?topicID=29.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/ffiresofheaven32084frm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=29.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/ffiresofheaven32084frm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=29.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="ri